      <h1 class="art-h1">How lenders assess blue-chip art as collateral</h1>
      <p class="art-lead">
        A significant painting can support liquidity without being sold — but only after it passes
        three tests. How identity, liquidity and control turn market evidence into a lending decision.
      </p>
      <div class="art-byline">
        <div class="art-author">
          <Image class="art-avatar" src={specialistImg} alt="" widths={[42, 84]} sizes="42px" format="webp" quality={80} />
